org.apache.poi.ddf

Class UnknownEscherRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.ddf.EscherRecord
      • org.apache.poi.ddf.UnknownEscherRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Duplicatable, GenericRecord 

    public final class UnknownEscherRecord
extends EscherRecord
    This record is used whenever a escher record is encountered that we do not explicitly support.(每当遇到我们不明确支持的escher记录时，就会使用此记录。)
